<br>
While they were talking, Andrya couldn’t help but smile. He was such a good conversationalist and kept a boring topic very interesting. She knew she could talk to him for hours on end. She noticed how when he talked, his words were full of life, and his voice a strong confidence to it. She adored that about him, it made her think about how she sounded.<br>
<br>
 Did she sound confident like that, or did she sound shy and unstable?  Were her conversations boring, or fun? Andrya stopped worrying about herself so she could enjoy his company and her meal.<br>
<br>
Once they had both finished, Jacob stood up. His clothes looked really good; she loved the color black against his skin. He walked over to her seat and pulled it out while taking her hand and leading her to another room. <p>--------<br>
